  "commit_message": "new_installer.py: clarify intent of install policy (#52460)\n\nClarify why we start with a `cache_only` policy if the user request is\n`auto`.\n\nThe other removed comment related to locks is a bit out of place, since\nthe sub-process isn't responsible for locks, so there's no reason to\nworry about them in that place.\n\nSigned-off-by: Harmen Stoppels <me@harmenstoppels.nl>",
